title: Ep 2419 - Jethalal in Trouble
shortDesc: Jethalal presumes Iyer to be Sunder, since Iyer is wearing Sunder’s cap. He applies permanent color on Iyer’s face, making Iyer furious. Iyer discovers that the color is not washing away with water. What happens now, watch this episode to find out.

title: Ep 2420 - Iyer is Furious
shortDesc: Jethalal calls up Sunder to find a solution but Sunder does not answer the phone. An helpless Jethalal takes the help of Taarak Mehta, who calls up Sunder.

title: Ep 2421 -
shortDesc: Jethalal gets to know that the colour on Iyer's face will take a month to wash off. Jethalal again is in a big trouble and decides to call Sunder. Watch th episode to know more.

title: Ep 2422 - When Every Plan Fails
shortDesc: The Gokuldham society members are trying their best to help Iyer in removing the color from his face. Each member suggests an idea, which ultimately fails. Finally, Sodhi comes up with a plan to help Iyer. Will Iyer reach the conference?

title: Ep 2423 - Chaos Over Some Colour
shortDesc: Everyone is bringing in their own idea to remove the colour from Iyer’s face. The photographer is on what seems like an endless wait and the time slot for Iyer to go for is international conference is closing in.

title: Ep 2424 - Tappu Solves the Problem
shortDesc: Iyer tries every solution but it fails to remove the color from his face. Just when Iyer gives up, Tappu arrives and assures that he has a solution.

title: Ep 2425 - Iyers Disappointment
shortDesc: Iyer is informed by his boss that he has to leave for the conference that evening. This hampers Iyer’s plan, who had decided to visit a skin specialist to remove color from his face.

title: Ep 2426 - Moms remedy
shortDesc: Iyer has to remove the colour off of his face before 7 if he is to go to US. Jethalal comes up with a peculiar idea to remove the colour. Will it work and will Iyer be able to go? Watch to find out!

title: Ep 2427 - Jethalals Final Solution
shortDesc: While on their way to find the cure for Iyer’s problem, Jethalal and co. are stopped by Chalu Pandey. After convincing Chalu Pandey, Jethalal finds the cow dung and gets it to Iyer. Will this solution work? Watch this episode to find out.

title: Ep 2428 - Jethalals Joy
shortDesc: Jethalal is worried that the artificial color on Iyer’s face will not be removed and hides in his house. To everyone's sunrise, the color is removed from Iyer’s face and he gets to go to the conference.

title: Ep 2429 - The Phone Call
shortDesc: Iyer returns from conference and is excited to be back in Gokuldham society. Meanwhile, Jethalal receives a call from Baga. But, before Jethalal can answer it, Baga cuts the call. Why has Baga called up Jethalal? Watch this episode to find out.

title: Ep 2430 - Bhaghas dilemma
shortDesc: Bhagha needs a half day off to spend with his girlfriend but Jethalal refuses to give in. Jethalal is at the society sharing sweets with everyone. What will happen to Bhagha’s relationship? Watch to find out.

title: Ep 2431 - The Deadline
shortDesc: Nattu Kaka tries to convince Bhagha’s girlfriend that he can’t get off of work that day, but her adamant attitude gives Bhagha a deadline for their love life if he wasn’t to go with her for a movie.

title: Ep 2432 - Bagas Leave
shortDesc: Baga pretends to be sick in order to get a day off from work. But, Jethalal learns that Baga is going out on a movie date and asks him to stay. Then, Baga claims that he has hurt his back and needs to go to the hospital.

title: Ep 2433 - Jethalals Surprise
shortDesc: Bagha decides to quit as Jethalal is not letting him take a leave. To Bagha’s surprise, Jethalal has planned a special surprise for him. While at the shop, Bavri arrives and informs Bagha that Jethalal has funded their special date.
